	<main>
		<section>
			<ul>
				<li>Co-founder of <a href="https://customeros.ai" target="_blank">CustomerOS</a></li>
				<li>Building AI sales, marketing and customer success Agents with <a href="https://mateocafe.com/" target="_blank">Matt Brown</a></li>
